folder: Degraw Street & Hicks Street, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Degraw Street, north side, from Hicks Street to Tiffany Place, shown in a sey of two views. In the center of the block is the Roman Catholic Church of the Sacred Heart of Jesus and Mary. To its left is the H. Behr plant.

P. L. Sperr

January 10, 1941
Views 1,2
